Title: Aubrey
Plot: When a detective mysteriously uncovers the remains of an FBI agent who disappeared in the 1940s while investigating a similar murder case to one she is now on, Mulder and Scully believe that the original killer had passed his genetic trait of violence to his grandchild.
GuestStars: Deborah Strang, Morgan Woodward, Terry O'Quinn, Joy Coghill, Robyn Driscoll, Peter Flemming, Sarah Jane Redmond, Emanuel Hajek
